# My Cybersecurity Notes

This is where I write down everything I learn about cybersecurity — OverTheWire walkthroughs, CTF writeups, and random security stuff I figure out along the way.

I'm Ihtisham, a 4th-semester cybersecurity student at AWKUM. This site is my digital notebook.

> **Live Site:** [ihtishamaliamir.github.io](https://ihtishamaliamir.github.io)

